WEBVTT

00:01:53.480 --> 00:01:55.519
I think we should stop this, Second Brother.

00:01:56.280 --> 00:01:57.159
Look at Weiguo.

00:01:57.159 --> 00:01:58.560
He's such a sincere guy.

00:01:58.719 --> 00:02:00.640
I want to see how long he can keep this up.

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:03.959
Fine, you guys can fight all you want.

00:02:03.959 --> 00:02:04.959
I just have one request.

00:02:04.959 --> 00:02:06.359
Don't ruin my deal, okay?

00:02:06.359 --> 00:02:07.280
Go on, get out of here.

00:02:07.640 --> 00:02:09.960
Hey, whose side are you on now?

00:02:11.080 --> 00:02:12.560
I think you're in a dangerous position.

00:02:12.560 --> 00:02:13.639
Do you want to help Ma Weiguo

00:02:13.639 --> 00:02:14.400
deal with us, is that it?

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:15.240
No, I don't, Brother.

00:02:15.240 --> 00:02:17.680
Traitors don't end well, you know that?

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:18.879
I'm not a traitor, Brother.

00:02:18.879 --> 00:02:19.520
Shut up.

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:21.360
After I drive Ma Weiguo away,

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:22.599
I'll deal with you back home.

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:25.599
Deal with me? Why would you deal with me?

00:02:25.919 --> 00:02:26.560
Let's go.

00:02:27.520 --> 00:02:28.639
Listen, Boss Ma.

00:02:28.960 --> 00:02:31.280
This place is indeed a bit expensive.

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:33.599
If you're having difficulties,

00:02:33.599 --> 00:02:34.879
don't force yourself.

00:02:35.599 --> 00:02:37.599
Alright, stop messing around.

00:02:38.599 --> 00:02:39.280
Qiu'er.

00:02:39.759 --> 00:02:41.400
You've seen quite a few houses these past days.

00:02:41.400 --> 00:02:42.319
Give us your opinion.

00:02:43.759 --> 00:02:45.159
We're all smart people here.

00:02:45.759 --> 00:02:47.120
I'll speak frankly.

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:48.520
I know exactly

00:02:48.599 --> 00:02:49.479
what you're thinking.

00:02:49.960 --> 00:02:50.919
And don't take us to see

00:02:50.919 --> 00:02:52.319
any more fancy villas.

00:02:52.520 --> 00:02:54.199
I think this one is acceptable.

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:56.400
If you agree, I'll pay in full.

00:02:56.599 --> 00:02:57.599
If you don't think it's good,

00:02:57.599 --> 00:02:58.439
then let's forget this whole thing.

00:02:58.439 --> 00:02:59.719
No, no, no, wait!

00:02:59.719 --> 00:03:01.879
This must cost over twenty million.

00:03:02.319 --> 00:03:04.360
Some people just can't stand

00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:06.199
seeing you get such a huge benefit.

00:03:07.479 --> 00:03:08.919
Don't listen to him, Qiu'er.

00:03:08.919 --> 00:03:09.960
He's trying to drive a wedge between us.

00:03:09.960 --> 00:03:11.960
Qiu'er, stand up straight.

00:03:12.639 --> 00:03:14.159
If you let him use this money

00:03:14.159 --> 00:03:15.120
to knock you down,

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:16.879
you'll never be able to stand tall again.

00:03:16.879 --> 00:03:18.080
My back's never been straight, Brother.

00:03:18.240 --> 00:03:20.120
Make up your mind, be decisive.

00:03:20.520 --> 00:03:21.520
Twenty million.

00:03:21.520 --> 00:03:22.520
I can give it to someone else just as easily.

00:03:22.520 --> 00:03:24.080
If you don't want it, I'll give it to someone else.

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:25.560
No, no, no, don't!

00:03:27.879 --> 00:03:28.919
Let's do it.

00:03:30.639 --> 00:03:31.520
This is the one.

00:03:31.879 --> 00:03:33.159
It's really quite good.

00:03:33.159 --> 00:03:34.120
I want this house.

00:03:34.120 --> 00:03:35.520
I think it's great, really.

00:03:35.520 --> 00:03:36.479
Don't try to stop me.

00:03:36.479 --> 00:03:37.919
I'll get mad at anyone who tries.

00:03:42.680 --> 00:03:43.560
That's it.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:49.159
The door's over here.

00:03:53.479 --> 00:03:56.240
Why did my dad hide it so well?

00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:00.919
Found it.

00:04:13.199 --> 00:04:14.319
What is this thing?

00:04:14.319 --> 00:04:15.360
It's a good thing!

00:04:15.840 --> 00:04:18.120
Sis, we need to go to your room to look at this.

00:04:18.120 --> 00:04:19.560
It's not good if my dad sees it.

00:04:19.560 --> 00:04:20.399
Come on, hurry up.

00:04:29.480 --> 00:04:30.199
Weiguo.

00:04:30.319 --> 00:04:32.240
I'll go back and have my parents move out.

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:34.399
I promise to vacate the house for you.

00:04:34.560 --> 00:04:36.199
I'll clean it up spotless for you.

00:04:36.199 --> 00:04:38.079
So you can live comfortably.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:41.600
Or how about I come over every noon and evening

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:42.839
to cook for you?

00:04:42.959 --> 00:04:43.720
You living alone,

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:45.360
all these miscellaneous chores

00:04:45.360 --> 00:04:47.199
aren't suitable for you to do yourself.

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:48.920
Quit your job.

00:04:50.079 --> 00:04:51.439
Quit your job,

00:04:51.439 --> 00:04:52.800
and when Auntie moves in,

00:04:52.800 --> 00:04:54.000
you can take good care of her.

00:04:54.319 --> 00:04:56.519
You can even learn some acupuncture or massage.

00:04:56.519 --> 00:04:57.800
Auntie could use that anytime.

00:04:57.959 --> 00:04:59.600
Taking care of Auntie is no problem.

00:04:59.600 --> 00:05:00.360
But my job, I...

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:01.560
I'll give you a sum of money.

00:05:01.920 --> 00:05:03.720
Consider it your salary, okay?

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:04.920
Is five hundred thousand a year enough?

00:05:10.399 --> 00:05:11.279
Weiguo.

00:05:13.079 --> 00:05:14.480
My mom is also free.

00:05:14.560 --> 00:05:17.120
How about both of us come work for you?

00:05:17.240 --> 00:05:18.480
Count it as two salaries.

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:20.199
Or one and a half is fine too.

00:05:30.079 --> 00:05:31.639
Get down here, get down!

00:05:34.920 --> 00:05:37.279
I mean, why are you being so servile?

00:05:37.279 --> 00:05:38.560
Can't you see?

00:05:38.639 --> 00:05:40.439
He's using money to humiliate you.

00:05:40.439 --> 00:05:42.319
And you're groveling. Isn't it shameful?

00:05:42.639 --> 00:05:43.959
How is it humiliating me?

00:05:43.959 --> 00:05:44.920
I think it's great.

00:05:44.920 --> 00:05:46.639
I... I need money right now.

00:05:47.480 --> 00:05:48.839
My dad's treatment costs money, right?

00:05:48.920 --> 00:05:50.639
Xiaoshi having a baby costs money, right?

00:05:50.639 --> 00:05:52.000
Me getting a bigger house costs money, right?

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:54.000
I can't get promoted now, I have no money.

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:55.439
I wish someone would humiliate me with money.

00:05:55.439 --> 00:05:56.800
Go ahead and humiliate me.

00:05:57.120 --> 00:05:59.000
I feel ashamed just being with you.

00:06:00.199 --> 00:06:01.000
What's wrong with that?

00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:03.720
It's easy for you all to talk.

00:06:03.720 --> 00:06:05.279
Big Brother, you have a huge roast duck restaurant.

00:06:05.279 --> 00:06:06.920
You won't starve even if you do nothing.

00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:07.720
Second Brother, you...

00:06:07.720 --> 00:06:08.959
You have so many apartments inside the Third and Fourth Ring Roads.

00:06:08.959 --> 00:06:10.240
And me? I have nothing.

00:06:10.240 --> 00:06:10.959
This is an opportunity.

00:06:10.959 --> 00:06:12.040
I have to seize it.

00:06:12.040 --> 00:06:13.000
Is this an opportunity?

00:06:13.399 --> 00:06:14.639
It's a trap.

00:06:16.480 --> 00:06:18.519
Don't look at me, I can't be bothered to lecture you.

00:06:19.240 --> 00:06:20.720
Alright then, let me say one more thing.

00:06:20.720 --> 00:06:22.240
I... I think Weiguo is a good person.

00:06:22.240 --> 00:06:23.160
He came back and helped me

00:06:23.160 --> 00:06:23.920
solve this urgent problem.

00:06:23.920 --> 00:06:24.600
Without a second thought,

00:06:24.600 --> 00:06:25.959
he settled the house matter for me.

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:27.560
Let me say something unpleasant too.

00:06:27.560 --> 00:06:28.560
Big Brother, Second Brother, tell me.

00:06:29.079 --> 00:06:30.079
We've known each other for almost forty years.

00:06:30.079 --> 00:06:31.439
You... you've never thought about

00:06:31.439 --> 00:06:32.680
helping me with this, have you?

00:06:37.879 --> 00:06:39.040
From now on, when you go out,

00:06:39.040 --> 00:06:40.480
don't say you're my brother.

00:06:41.199 --> 00:06:43.079
Hey, why are you getting angry again?

00:06:43.079 --> 00:06:44.199
I... I didn't mean it that way.

00:06:44.199 --> 00:06:45.120
Cut the crap.

00:06:45.120 --> 00:06:46.240
Get that guy down from there.

00:06:46.240 --> 00:06:48.000
I... I... I really... I...

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:48.560
Wait.

00:06:48.879 --> 00:06:50.040
Ma Weiguo, get down!

00:06:50.040 --> 00:06:50.560
I really...

00:06:51.199 --> 00:06:51.920
Brother.

00:06:53.319 --> 00:06:53.920
I...

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:10.199
Weiguo, what are you doing?

00:07:10.199 --> 00:07:10.759
This...

00:07:15.959 --> 00:07:16.519
Welcome

00:07:16.519 --> 00:07:18.439
Welcome, welcome, welcome.

00:07:19.360 --> 00:07:20.120
This is...

00:07:20.120 --> 00:07:21.360
Is this the four of them?

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.240
Yeah, look.

00:07:23.279 --> 00:07:24.600
The one with long hair is...

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:26.040
So cool.

00:07:26.040 --> 00:07:26.519
That's my dad.

00:07:26.519 --> 00:07:27.720
This is Uncle Wang.

00:07:28.279 --> 00:07:29.839
He was pretty flashy back in the day too.

00:07:29.839 --> 00:07:31.279
Long hair, and wearing sunglasses.

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:33.600
Let me see.

00:07:35.480 --> 00:07:36.319
Who's this?

00:07:36.319 --> 00:07:38.040
This little... this kid is...

00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:38.600
Uncle Qiu.

00:07:38.600 --> 00:07:39.279
Uncle Qiu.

00:07:39.519 --> 00:07:40.519
So charming.

00:07:40.519 --> 00:07:41.759
And with two girls.

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:44.079
But still pretty cool.

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:49.720
This is a gift for you.

00:07:50.399 --> 00:07:51.800
He even gave a gift.

00:07:52.360 --> 00:07:53.319
That's nice.

00:07:57.319 --> 00:07:58.160
What are you looking at?

00:08:00.079 --> 00:08:00.920
Let me see.

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:05.439
My dear Tong Qiu,

00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:09.279
you are the handsomest guy in our alley.

00:08:35.480 --> 00:08:37.159
I was just afraid Big Brother and Second Brother

00:08:37.159 --> 00:08:38.519
would mess this up for me.

00:08:38.759 --> 00:08:40.519
Ma Weiguo is still the most domineering.

00:08:40.519 --> 00:08:41.679
He didn't even blink.

00:08:41.679 --> 00:08:43.039
He just agreed to it.

00:08:51.399 --> 00:08:52.679
Let me interview you three.

00:08:52.960 --> 00:08:54.360
Why aren't you excited?

00:08:54.919 --> 00:08:56.840
We're about to live in a villa.

00:08:56.840 --> 00:08:58.039
A detached one.

00:09:00.679 --> 00:09:03.399
Why is Ma Weiguo giving you a villa?

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:05.440
This sounds fishy to me.

00:09:05.440 --> 00:09:07.360
Mom, just relax.

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:09.559
He wants me to take care of Auntie in her old age.

00:09:09.559 --> 00:09:11.840
You dare ask for a villa for such a small thing?

00:09:11.960 --> 00:09:13.600
Ma Weiguo and I have been friends for so many years.

00:09:13.600 --> 00:09:15.679
Don't you know how deep our friendship is?

00:09:15.679 --> 00:09:18.960
Food handed out in contempt will give you a stomachache.

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:23.840
What's wrong with you three?

00:09:24.200 --> 00:09:24.840
Dad.

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:27.159
Could you please not get angry first?

00:09:27.759 --> 00:09:28.519
I get it.

00:09:28.519 --> 00:09:30.960
Are you afraid you won't get used to living in a villa?

00:09:31.360 --> 00:09:32.799
Can't we just try it out first?

00:09:32.799 --> 00:09:34.519
If it really doesn't work out, we can sell the villa later.

00:09:34.519 --> 00:09:35.799
It's worth tens of millions.

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:37.519
We can lie down sideways, lie down lengthwise...

00:09:37.519 --> 00:09:39.120
What difference does it make how we lie down?

00:09:43.159 --> 00:09:44.799
So what if I didn't get promoted?

00:09:44.799 --> 00:09:46.000
I'll even quit my job then.

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:46.399
I'm done.

00:09:46.399 --> 00:09:47.000
What?

00:09:47.639 --> 00:09:49.480
So you didn't get promoted after all?

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:50.919
You lied to us.

00:09:51.240 --> 00:09:53.080
No, no, no, no, no.

00:09:53.399 --> 00:09:54.399
Alright.

00:09:57.480 --> 00:09:58.720
Dad, Mom.

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:00.000
Don't get angry yet.

00:10:00.559 --> 00:10:01.519
I, I, I admit it.

00:10:01.519 --> 00:10:03.879
I did lie to you before.

00:10:03.879 --> 00:10:05.440
But I meant well.

00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:09.000
I apologize, I apologize.

00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:11.240
But that doesn't matter now.

00:10:11.240 --> 00:10:11.799
Dad.

00:10:11.879 --> 00:10:13.519
Then you can use the best medicine.

00:10:13.519 --> 00:10:14.720
Take as much as you want.

00:10:14.720 --> 00:10:16.039
Don't hold back at all.

00:10:16.039 --> 00:10:16.720
Mom.

00:10:16.799 --> 00:10:18.120
You've worked hard all these years.

00:10:18.120 --> 00:10:19.279
We'll hire a maid for you then.

00:10:19.279 --> 00:10:20.840
You can rest properly and enjoy life.

00:10:21.600 --> 00:10:22.279
Wife.

00:10:22.759 --> 00:10:24.320
Let's not go to Xi'an.

00:10:24.399 --> 00:10:26.080
If necessary, we'll quit that job.

00:10:26.080 --> 00:10:27.240
We'll just stay home peacefully.

00:10:27.240 --> 00:10:28.320
Focus on having a baby.

00:10:33.279 --> 00:10:35.200
This guy is going crazy.

00:10:35.600 --> 00:10:37.200
You stop right there, stop!

00:10:37.200 --> 00:10:38.000
Stop!

00:10:38.440 --> 00:10:39.759
You brat!

00:10:39.759 --> 00:10:41.799
Look at your sorry self.

00:10:41.799 --> 00:10:43.879
You were almost kneeling to him.

00:10:43.879 --> 00:10:46.120
Your legs went weak over a villa.

00:10:46.679 --> 00:10:48.200
What did I teach you when you were little?

00:10:48.200 --> 00:10:49.960
Did you study all those years for nothing?

00:10:50.679 --> 00:10:51.480
Enough.

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:53.120
You... you...

00:10:53.120 --> 00:10:54.960
Fine, you didn't get promoted.

00:10:54.960 --> 00:10:56.720
Why did you lie to us?

00:10:56.919 --> 00:10:59.200
Yes, not getting promoted was my fault.

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:00.679
But we have a villa now.

00:11:00.679 --> 00:11:02.440
Is getting promoted really that important?

00:11:02.440 --> 00:11:04.200
Even a small thing like a promotion...

00:11:04.200 --> 00:11:06.679
...is earned by your own ability.

00:11:06.799 --> 00:11:07.679
So what?

00:11:07.799 --> 00:11:09.840
Shouldn't you take care of Auntie?

00:11:09.840 --> 00:11:11.279
How dare you ask for his villa?

00:11:11.279 --> 00:11:12.159
Come on, come on.

00:11:12.360 --> 00:11:13.360
Come, come.

00:11:13.519 --> 00:11:15.080
Go take a piss, take a piss...

00:11:15.080 --> 00:11:15.879
...and take a look, take a look...

00:11:15.879 --> 00:11:17.840
...see what kind of person you are!

00:11:18.679 --> 00:11:20.039
You're going to be the death of me.

00:11:24.799 --> 00:11:25.720
Alright, alright.

00:11:25.720 --> 00:11:27.360
Be careful, you're still sick.

00:11:27.360 --> 00:11:27.799
You really are...

00:11:27.799 --> 00:11:29.559
Sick? Then just die from it.

00:11:29.559 --> 00:11:31.639
Stop the medicine, I won't take it.

00:11:31.639 --> 00:11:32.120
Dad.

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:32.639
You...

00:11:33.159 --> 00:11:34.240
I'm so angry.

00:11:35.679 --> 00:11:36.399
See?

00:11:36.720 --> 00:11:38.799
The family finally gets together for a meal...

00:11:39.360 --> 00:11:41.519
Alright, I'll go talk to your dad.

00:11:52.440 --> 00:11:54.279
You didn't even back me up.

00:11:54.279 --> 00:11:55.120
What could I say?

00:11:55.120 --> 00:11:56.519
You shouldn't have lied in the first place.

00:11:56.519 --> 00:11:57.799
How long can you keep this up?

00:11:57.799 --> 00:12:00.440
Yeah, every moment I can hide it is a win.

00:12:05.279 --> 00:12:07.279
My dear, don't be angry.

00:12:07.279 --> 00:12:08.759
We're about to live in a big villa.

00:12:08.759 --> 00:12:09.440
Our living situation...

00:12:09.440 --> 00:12:10.759
...is about to be solved, isn't it?

00:12:10.759 --> 00:12:11.679
Have you ever thought...

00:12:11.679 --> 00:12:12.639
...that when I said I wanted a villa,

00:12:12.639 --> 00:12:14.120
I meant through our own hard work.

00:12:14.120 --> 00:12:15.399
Not through someone else's charity.

00:12:15.399 --> 00:12:16.159
Yes, yes, yes.

00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:18.960
But Weiguo isn't just "someone else."

00:12:19.120 --> 00:12:20.720
It's not that I'm not trying.

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:22.559
I just don't want to play those dirty games.

00:12:22.559 --> 00:12:23.279
You have no idea...

00:12:23.279 --> 00:12:25.200
...the filthy stuff involved in promotions.

00:12:25.200 --> 00:12:26.519
I can't even be bothered to talk about it.

00:12:26.519 --> 00:12:28.320
You talk as if I've never had a job.

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:29.679
So, my promotion and raise in Xi'an...

00:12:29.679 --> 00:12:31.039
...were also through dirty means, right?

00:12:31.039 --> 00:12:31.960
No, no, that's not what I meant.

00:12:31.960 --> 00:12:32.639
Here you are.

00:12:32.639 --> 00:12:33.360
Uncle Wang.

00:12:33.360 --> 00:12:34.120
What can I get you?

00:12:34.120 --> 00:12:35.080
I need to get some water.

00:12:35.240 --> 00:12:36.159
Can you carry it?

00:12:36.159 --> 00:12:36.799
Yes.

00:12:38.639 --> 00:12:40.039
I really didn't mean it that way.

00:12:40.320 --> 00:12:41.639
I... I just think that right now...

00:12:41.639 --> 00:12:43.159
...improving our life is more important.

00:12:43.159 --> 00:12:44.120
I don't think you've grasped...

00:12:44.120 --> 00:12:45.559
...the main point at all.

00:12:45.559 --> 00:12:46.879
Yes, yes, we'll figure it out slowly.

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:48.759
Don't worry about it. Go pay.

00:12:53.519 --> 00:12:54.960
So I'm wrong again, huh?

00:12:59.480 --> 00:13:00.679
Young couple having a spat?

00:13:00.679 --> 00:13:02.879
N-no, we're fine.

00:13:03.600 --> 00:13:04.679
Here you go, here you go.

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:24.799
Uncle Wang.

00:13:25.919 --> 00:13:28.000
Sometimes I'm just so tired.

00:13:29.919 --> 00:13:32.360
Some people haven't even clocked out by 3 a.m.

00:13:33.759 --> 00:13:35.879
Some are already at work by 5 a.m.

00:13:38.440 --> 00:13:40.720
East, west, south, north, from the 4th to the 6th ring road.

00:13:42.120 --> 00:13:43.600
Boss Wang from Yanjiao.

00:13:44.559 --> 00:13:45.960
Lucy from Tiantongyuan.

00:13:46.960 --> 00:13:48.440
Vivian from Tongzhou.

00:13:50.039 --> 00:13:51.399
Andy from Yizhuang.

00:13:53.000 --> 00:13:54.639
Who isn't squeezing onto the subway...

00:13:55.720 --> 00:13:58.960
...for two hours at dawn to get to work?

00:14:01.519 --> 00:14:03.480
Who doesn't want to conquer the world?

00:14:10.279 --> 00:14:11.279
Tong Qiu.

00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:14.039
What are you drinking?

00:14:15.840 --> 00:14:16.720
Dayao.

00:14:21.799 --> 00:14:22.840
Have some lemon water.

00:14:24.360 --> 00:14:25.159
Thanks, sis.

00:14:25.159 --> 00:14:25.960
Tongtong, have some too.

00:14:25.960 --> 00:14:26.399
Okay.

00:14:29.639 --> 00:14:30.679
Oh, right, sis.

00:14:30.960 --> 00:14:33.360
I have a client who's an agent for this brand.

00:14:33.360 --> 00:14:34.480
They have an employee discount.

00:14:34.480 --> 00:14:36.320
I got one for each of you.

00:14:36.480 --> 00:14:38.679
You two have a lot of expenses right now.

00:14:38.679 --> 00:14:40.559
No, don't get one for me.

00:14:41.279 --> 00:14:41.799
Is it pretty?

00:14:41.799 --> 00:14:44.000
Thanks, Auntie. I like this one.

00:14:45.879 --> 00:14:48.039
It's with the discount, not expensive.

00:14:48.039 --> 00:14:48.879
Take a look.

00:14:49.159 --> 00:14:50.519
I love you so much, Auntie!

00:14:50.519 --> 00:14:51.600
I like this one.

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:53.159
It's pretty.

00:14:54.039 --> 00:14:54.799
Look at this.

00:14:54.879 --> 00:14:56.440
Sis, try it on.

00:14:57.240 --> 00:14:58.679
Alright, let me just look at it first.

00:15:04.519 --> 00:15:07.600
This... this is too, too expensive.

00:15:07.600 --> 00:15:08.919
It's not for someone like me.

00:15:09.480 --> 00:15:11.600
Sis, just try it on.

00:15:12.039 --> 00:15:14.600
I bet it'll look great on you.

00:15:14.600 --> 00:15:16.120
Try it, Auntie. See how it looks.

00:15:16.120 --> 00:15:16.720
Come on.

00:15:18.039 --> 00:15:19.840
See? Pretty, right?

00:15:19.840 --> 00:15:20.720
Pretty.

00:15:20.840 --> 00:15:21.559
It looks good, Auntie.

00:15:21.559 --> 00:15:22.159
Really pretty.

00:15:22.159 --> 00:15:22.960
It suits you so well.

00:15:22.960 --> 00:15:24.320
Look at this fabric. You can tell...

00:15:24.320 --> 00:15:25.639
...you can tell it's too expensive.

00:15:25.639 --> 00:15:26.519
I work every day.

00:15:26.519 --> 00:15:28.720
If I get oil on it, it'll be hard to wash.

00:15:28.720 --> 00:15:31.440
What I wear now is fine, practical for work.

00:15:31.919 --> 00:15:33.519
I'd have no chance to wear it.

00:15:34.080 --> 00:15:34.960
You haven't seen...

00:15:34.960 --> 00:15:37.000
...your aunt's photos from when she was young.

00:15:37.240 --> 00:15:38.919
Full of floral dresses and such.

00:15:38.919 --> 00:15:40.360
So stylish and beautiful.

00:15:40.360 --> 00:15:42.240
Really? I want to see the photos too.

00:15:42.240 --> 00:15:43.600
Everyone was young once.

00:15:43.600 --> 00:15:45.200
And she wasn't even showing off.

00:15:45.440 --> 00:15:47.279
Sis, just take it.

00:15:47.279 --> 00:15:48.679
We'll go out together sometime.

00:15:48.679 --> 00:15:49.919
You'll have a chance to wear it.

00:15:50.039 --> 00:15:52.519
Yeah, wear it for Uncle Wang then.

00:15:52.519 --> 00:15:54.840
I guarantee he'll be head over heels.

00:15:54.840 --> 00:15:57.279
Who has time to charm him?

00:15:57.279 --> 00:15:58.600
We're an old married couple.

00:15:58.600 --> 00:16:00.279
With his smell of duck grease all over...

00:16:00.279 --> 00:16:01.600
...I don't even want to smell it.

00:16:01.600 --> 00:16:03.120
And he can't be bothered to look at me.

00:16:03.879 --> 00:16:05.919
If I put this on...

00:16:05.919 --> 00:16:07.159
...I might scare him.

00:16:07.159 --> 00:16:08.799
He'll think I did something wrong.

00:16:08.799 --> 00:16:09.720
That wouldn't happen.

00:16:12.440 --> 00:16:13.360
It really is pretty.

00:16:22.559 --> 00:16:23.519
You startled me.

00:16:23.720 --> 00:16:24.519
Does it look good?

00:16:24.879 --> 00:16:25.840
Y-yes, good.

00:16:26.679 --> 00:16:27.799
Xiaoshi gave it to me.

00:16:28.440 --> 00:16:29.720
I was just thinking...

00:16:29.799 --> 00:16:31.159
...I don't usually wear things like this.

00:16:31.159 --> 00:16:33.320
Maybe I should give it back.

00:16:33.799 --> 00:16:35.120
Then give it back.

00:16:37.080 --> 00:16:39.000
You'd really give it back just because I said so?

00:16:39.159 --> 00:16:40.120
Then keep it.

00:16:41.200 --> 00:16:42.000
No, you...

00:16:42.919 --> 00:16:45.200
Look. Does it look good or not?

00:16:47.039 --> 00:16:49.519
Tell the truth. Think before you speak.

00:16:51.559 --> 00:16:51.960
This...

00:16:51.960 --> 00:16:53.200
Tell. The. Truth.

00:16:57.159 --> 00:16:57.759
This...

00:16:57.879 --> 00:17:00.039
Think carefully before you speak.

00:17:04.200 --> 00:17:06.039
No, I think this dress...

00:17:07.160 --> 00:17:08.559
Wh-what about it?

00:17:09.160 --> 00:17:10.160
...kinda looks like...

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:11.680
Wang Chunsheng, I'm warning you.

00:17:11.680 --> 00:17:13.440
If you say I look like a foot-washing, cupping therapist...

00:17:13.440 --> 00:17:14.519
...I'll tell Xiaoshi right now.

00:17:14.519 --> 00:17:15.400
Your big brother said...

00:17:15.400 --> 00:17:17.559
...this dress makes you look like a foot-washing, cupping therapist.

00:17:17.559 --> 00:17:18.599
No, but you... you...

00:17:18.599 --> 00:17:20.400
Weren't you the one who said to give it back?

00:17:20.640 --> 00:17:22.240
Why would I give it back? I...

00:17:23.480 --> 00:17:24.960
No, are you all crazy? Darn it.

00:17:24.960 --> 00:17:28.039
Who's crazy? Who's crazy here?

00:17:28.440 --> 00:17:31.000
Look at me. Do I look good?

00:17:31.400 --> 00:17:32.519
I'm going to pick up Feifei.

00:17:40.920 --> 00:17:42.000
Boring

00:17:45.240 --> 00:17:46.319
Isn't school over?

00:17:46.319 --> 00:17:48.039
I'm picking up my son, not a bad guy.

00:17:48.559 --> 00:17:49.640
Coming, coming.

00:17:50.119 --> 00:17:50.720
Alright.

00:17:51.440 --> 00:17:52.359
Tough job.

00:17:56.400 --> 00:17:57.319
Come here, Wang Fei.

00:18:00.119 --> 00:18:01.400
Why are you here again?

00:18:01.400 --> 00:18:02.480
What do you mean, 'why am I here again'?

00:18:02.480 --> 00:18:03.119
Didn't I tell you?

00:18:03.119 --> 00:18:04.599
From now on, I have to manage you.

00:18:04.599 --> 00:18:05.880
Seriously, when will this end?

00:18:05.880 --> 00:18:06.720
Hold on.

00:18:07.720 --> 00:18:08.640
I've studied it.

00:18:08.640 --> 00:18:10.680
Your study schedule.

00:18:11.319 --> 00:18:13.519
You're not exercising enough, you know?

00:18:13.519 --> 00:18:15.240
It's not good for your brain to rest.

00:18:15.720 --> 00:18:16.799
Alright then.

00:18:17.640 --> 00:18:18.759
Starting today,

00:18:18.880 --> 00:18:21.480
on the way home, I'll ride, you run.

00:18:22.079 --> 00:18:22.960
I run?

00:18:23.079 --> 00:18:23.920
I've been in class all day.

00:18:23.920 --> 00:18:25.200
Where do I get the energy to run?

00:18:25.559 --> 00:18:26.279
Listen, let me tell you.

00:18:26.279 --> 00:18:28.240
Back when I was into the gym,

00:18:28.240 --> 00:18:30.079
once you ran for twenty minutes,

00:18:30.079 --> 00:18:31.359
you wouldn't feel tired anymore.

00:18:31.359 --> 00:18:33.799
You just couldn't stop running, you know?

00:18:34.319 --> 00:18:35.759
Slow down, slow down!

00:18:36.079 --> 00:18:37.400
Watch for cars! Watch out!

00:18:43.000 --> 00:18:43.799
Hey, man.

00:18:44.480 --> 00:18:46.000
We've been walking the whole way.

00:18:46.279 --> 00:18:47.759
Can't you run a few steps?

00:18:52.680 --> 00:18:54.000
Run! Start running!

00:18:57.000 --> 00:18:58.559
What's the deal, man?

00:18:59.240 --> 00:19:01.319
Just a few more steps, turn the corner,

00:19:01.319 --> 00:19:02.599
and we're basically home.

00:19:02.599 --> 00:19:04.400
Can't you just run a few steps?

00:19:08.400 --> 00:19:10.400
I said I don't want to run.

00:19:10.400 --> 00:19:11.559
And I don't want to endure hardship.

00:19:11.559 --> 00:19:13.079
I'm not following your schedule either.

00:19:13.079 --> 00:19:13.640
What?

00:19:13.640 --> 00:19:16.200
Running a few steps counts as hardship to you?

00:19:16.200 --> 00:19:17.079
Our generation

00:19:17.079 --> 00:19:18.119
endured hardship all the way here.

00:19:18.119 --> 00:19:19.440
Why can't you endure a little hardship?

00:19:19.440 --> 00:19:19.920
Dad.

00:19:20.599 --> 00:19:22.640
Back in your day, conditions were bad.

00:19:22.640 --> 00:19:24.039
You *had* to endure hardship.

00:19:24.039 --> 00:19:25.200
Our generation is different.

00:19:25.200 --> 00:19:26.960
When I clearly don't need to, why would I

00:19:26.960 --> 00:19:28.279
go looking for hardship?

00:19:29.240 --> 00:19:30.519
Let me ask you one question.

00:19:31.079 --> 00:19:33.960
The shop, this house...

00:19:33.960 --> 00:19:35.799
You'll leave them all to me eventually, right?

00:19:38.440 --> 00:19:40.240
Don't you start eyeing that stuff.

00:19:40.240 --> 00:19:41.039
Then that's it, isn't it?

00:19:41.039 --> 00:19:42.000
Exactly.

00:19:42.000 --> 00:19:42.799
So from now on,

00:19:42.799 --> 00:19:44.319
I'll stop studying.

00:19:44.319 --> 00:19:45.559
In the future, I won't do anything.

00:19:45.559 --> 00:19:47.119
I'll still have a place to live, money to spend.

00:19:47.119 --> 00:19:48.240
Besides, I can do live streams now.

00:19:48.240 --> 00:19:49.519
I can earn money myself.

00:19:49.519 --> 00:19:50.519
I don't need to work hard at all.

00:19:50.519 --> 00:19:51.440
I can retire early

00:19:51.440 --> 00:19:52.480
and enjoy life.

00:19:52.480 --> 00:19:54.039
This so-called live streaming of yours

00:19:54.039 --> 00:19:56.079
is all temporary, you know?

00:19:56.079 --> 00:19:57.200
Fine, it's temporary.

00:19:57.200 --> 00:19:58.400
Then let me put it another way.

00:19:58.839 --> 00:19:59.920
If I do as you say,

00:20:00.519 --> 00:20:02.480
struggle and grind through my studies,

00:20:02.559 --> 00:20:03.759
get a PhD,

00:20:04.279 --> 00:20:05.440
graduate in the future,

00:20:05.440 --> 00:20:06.720
get a job at a big tech company,

00:20:06.720 --> 00:20:08.400
then work 996, competing with everyone,

00:20:08.400 --> 00:20:09.799
grind until I'm over forty,

00:20:09.799 --> 00:20:10.880
my hair's gone,

00:20:10.880 --> 00:20:12.240
skin's dry, face full of wrinkles.

00:20:12.240 --> 00:20:13.039
What's it all for?

00:20:13.039 --> 00:20:14.119
What's the goal?

00:20:14.119 --> 00:20:15.799
Isn't it still to retire early and enjoy life?

00:20:15.799 --> 00:20:16.759
I can achieve that right now.

00:20:16.759 --> 00:20:18.400
Don't give me this useless talk.

00:20:18.480 --> 00:20:20.160
Prove yourself by getting into university first.

00:20:20.160 --> 00:20:22.680
Then talk about your PhD plans.

00:20:22.799 --> 00:20:24.160
You right now,

00:20:24.160 --> 00:20:25.519
you've been brainwashed

00:20:25.519 --> 00:20:26.799
by those online 'lying flat' types.

00:20:26.799 --> 00:20:28.319
Brainwashed, you know?

00:20:28.319 --> 00:20:29.960
If you start slacking off like this now,

00:20:29.960 --> 00:20:31.960
your whole life will be ruined.

00:20:34.079 --> 00:20:34.880
Ruined?

00:20:36.440 --> 00:20:37.880
I'm not breaking any laws.

00:20:37.960 --> 00:20:39.079
I'm not doing anything bad.

00:20:39.519 --> 00:20:41.759
I just want to live my one life well.

00:20:41.920 --> 00:20:43.000
That counts as ruined?

00:20:51.359 --> 00:20:51.880
So what?

00:20:51.880 --> 00:20:54.079
I was the one who reported the cafe tutoring class.

00:20:54.200 --> 00:20:55.920
I heard you talking with Second Uncle.

00:20:56.039 --> 00:20:56.960
You stop right there!

00:20:57.599 --> 00:20:58.279
What?

00:20:58.759 --> 00:21:00.240
What did you say, you little brat?

00:21:01.160 --> 00:21:02.599
You reported it?

00:21:02.960 --> 00:21:04.279
I'm telling you, acting like this,

00:21:04.279 --> 00:21:06.559
you'll ruin that cafe, you know?

00:21:06.559 --> 00:21:08.480
Think of all the people working there.

00:21:08.480 --> 00:21:10.799
They'll lose their jobs, you know?

00:21:15.960 --> 00:21:16.880
You hit me?

00:21:17.720 --> 00:21:19.400
Fine, hit me. Go on, hit me again.

00:21:19.400 --> 00:21:20.279
All you know is hitting.

00:21:20.279 --> 00:21:21.759
Serves you right for fighting and going to jail.

00:21:25.039 --> 00:21:26.880
I won't leave you a single cent.

00:21:27.000 --> 00:21:29.240
Even when I die, I'll donate it all.

00:21:30.920 --> 00:21:31.759
Go ahead and donate.

00:21:31.880 --> 00:21:33.519
Donate it to whoever you want.

00:21:46.680 --> 00:21:47.480
Go away!

00:22:31.920 --> 00:22:33.640
Wang Chunsheng, how could you really hit him?

00:22:34.000 --> 00:22:35.519
How can you be so unreasonable?

00:22:35.680 --> 00:22:37.559
If you hurt our son, I'll fight you to the death.

00:22:38.400 --> 00:22:40.039
*I'm* the one feeling awful here.

00:22:41.440 --> 00:22:43.680
What's going on?

00:22:45.839 --> 00:22:48.000
But you still can't hit your son.

00:22:49.359 --> 00:22:50.920
This incident,

00:22:51.599 --> 00:22:53.519
I'll never get over it.

00:23:09.079 --> 00:23:10.640
I remember one year,

00:23:10.839 --> 00:23:12.000
my old man

00:23:12.000 --> 00:23:13.319
also in the alley,

00:23:13.319 --> 00:23:15.759
kicked over his Phoenix brand bicycle

00:23:16.160 --> 00:23:17.599
and slapped me.

00:23:17.720 --> 00:23:19.319
Pointed at my nose and said,

00:23:19.759 --> 00:23:20.960
Darn it.

00:23:33.400 --> 00:23:34.319
Another year,

00:23:34.559 --> 00:23:35.440
I said,

00:23:35.599 --> 00:23:38.759
"You're the most failed father I've ever seen."

00:23:40.079 --> 00:23:41.200
He laughed after hearing that.

00:23:41.319 --> 00:23:42.839
Pointed at my nose and said,

00:23:44.079 --> 00:23:44.920
"Kid,

00:23:45.359 --> 00:23:46.920
we'll see about that."

00:23:50.519 --> 00:23:51.839
We'll see.

00:24:17.319 --> 00:24:19.079
Why aren't the lights off?

00:24:22.319 --> 00:24:24.480
And you didn't take off your headphones.

00:24:27.519 --> 00:24:28.480
Feifei.

00:25:03.559 --> 00:25:05.599
Actually, about me hitting you...

00:25:08.440 --> 00:25:09.960
Deep down inside,

00:25:12.359 --> 00:25:14.279
why should I apologize to you?

00:25:14.599 --> 00:25:15.920
I'm your father.

00:25:18.240 --> 00:25:20.200
A father hitting his son is justified.

00:25:23.640 --> 00:25:25.279
And I haven't hit you that many times.

00:25:29.160 --> 00:25:30.400
But I also know

00:25:31.559 --> 00:25:33.039
that from now on, outside,

00:25:35.519 --> 00:25:37.000
I should save you some face.

00:25:37.440 --> 00:25:39.279
I'll avoid hitting you if I can.

00:25:59.240 --> 00:26:00.680
So you're starting to feel bad for him?

00:26:01.240 --> 00:26:03.440
Why would I feel bad for him?

00:26:05.640 --> 00:26:06.880
But this kid...

00:26:07.599 --> 00:26:09.680
just look at that fiery spirit.

00:26:10.160 --> 00:26:11.599
He's definitely my own flesh and blood.

00:26:11.599 --> 00:26:13.240
That goes without saying.

00:26:15.119 --> 00:26:16.039
Let's go, let's go.

00:26:49.000 --> 00:26:50.960
Branch Manager, you're back.

00:26:52.759 --> 00:26:53.359
Sit.

00:26:58.400 --> 00:26:59.480
Old Tong,

00:27:00.079 --> 00:27:01.559
I remember you have

00:27:01.559 --> 00:27:03.359
a few long-term clients, right?

00:27:03.720 --> 00:27:05.839
Yes, those old clients.

00:27:05.839 --> 00:27:07.519
I've maintained them quite well.

00:27:07.880 --> 00:27:09.160
Hand them over.

00:27:09.759 --> 00:27:10.839
Transfer these clients

00:27:10.839 --> 00:27:12.279
to Xiao Jia.

00:27:14.680 --> 00:27:15.519
Why?

00:27:15.839 --> 00:27:16.640
And also,

00:27:17.119 --> 00:27:18.039
your tardiness and leaving early

00:27:18.039 --> 00:27:20.079
have been far too frequent lately.

00:27:20.079 --> 00:27:21.359
It's created a very bad impression.

00:27:22.039 --> 00:27:24.000
Your bonus for the second half of the year is canceled.

00:27:25.119 --> 00:27:26.119
You... this...

00:27:26.799 --> 00:27:28.359
This is... too sudden.

00:27:28.559 --> 00:27:29.599
Wh-why?

00:27:29.599 --> 00:27:30.920
You ask me why?

00:27:31.759 --> 00:27:33.480
How many chances have I given you?

00:27:34.279 --> 00:27:35.640
They were practically begging to meet with you,

00:27:35.640 --> 00:27:36.799
and you showed them zero respect.

00:27:36.880 --> 00:27:38.359
And you still ask me why?

00:27:39.279 --> 00:27:41.200
You're the important one, you're the precious one.

00:27:41.200 --> 00:27:41.839
No, no, no.

00:27:41.839 --> 00:27:42.240
Get out.

00:27:42.240 --> 00:27:42.720
It's not that, sir...

00:27:59.359 --> 00:28:00.799
Let me wash that for you.

00:28:17.519 --> 00:28:18.279
Honey.

00:28:22.559 --> 00:28:24.680
I know you're in a bad mood right now,

00:28:26.599 --> 00:28:27.880
but my thing about going to Xi'an

00:28:27.880 --> 00:28:29.240
really can't be delayed any longer.

00:28:29.240 --> 00:28:30.640
I need to give them an answer soon.

00:28:30.640 --> 00:28:32.440
What are you actually thinking?

00:28:34.680 --> 00:28:35.960
Why go to Xi'an?

00:28:35.960 --> 00:28:36.680
What a hassle.

00:28:36.680 --> 00:28:38.079
I'm about to get a promotion soon.

00:28:38.079 --> 00:28:38.559
Don't go.

00:28:38.559 --> 00:28:39.720
You're always talking about a promotion.

00:28:39.720 --> 00:28:40.960
How many years has it been?

00:28:41.079 --> 00:28:43.319
Besides one raise of less than two hundred yuan

00:28:43.319 --> 00:28:44.440
and a bellyful of anger,

00:28:44.440 --> 00:28:45.400
what promotion have you gotten?

00:28:46.400 --> 00:28:48.680
How are we supposed to provide for a child like this?

00:28:49.119 --> 00:28:49.839
Brother Wang.

00:28:49.839 --> 00:28:51.720
Could you please send me the quote

00:28:51.720 --> 00:28:53.319
for our old house? Thank you.

00:28:56.359 --> 00:28:57.720
You raise a child according to your means.

00:28:57.720 --> 00:28:58.960
If you're poor, you raise them one way; if you're rich, another.

00:28:58.960 --> 00:29:00.440
Besides, look at Big Brother.

00:29:00.440 --> 00:29:02.440
A few years ago, he wasn't even earning as much as us.

00:29:02.440 --> 00:29:03.920
Didn't Feifei still grow up fine?

00:29:04.720 --> 00:29:06.359
Then why don't you compare yourself to Second Brother?

00:29:06.359 --> 00:29:07.599
Or Sister Qian?

00:29:08.279 --> 00:29:09.880
Their kids, Yuanyuan and Xuanxuan,

00:29:10.200 --> 00:29:12.440
are learning piano, learning painting,

00:29:12.960 --> 00:29:14.799
and often go abroad to broaden their horizons.

00:29:14.960 --> 00:29:15.680
Our child

00:29:15.680 --> 00:29:17.319
can't fall behind at the starting line either.

00:29:18.200 --> 00:29:19.799
Alright, thanks, Brother Wang.

00:29:20.759 --> 00:29:21.839
Tong Qiu.

00:29:23.240 --> 00:29:24.599
Let's not argue.

00:29:24.880 --> 00:29:26.119
What happens in the future,

00:29:26.119 --> 00:29:27.000
no one can predict.

00:29:27.000 --> 00:29:28.119
Worrying about it now is useless.

00:29:28.119 --> 00:29:29.440
Don't just brush me off like this.

00:29:29.920 --> 00:29:31.480
Alright, alright, alright, let's sleep.

00:29:31.960 --> 00:29:33.799
No, no, no, you get up.

00:29:33.799 --> 00:29:34.359
Go to sleep now.

00:29:34.359 --> 00:29:36.039
You need to think about the future too.

00:29:36.480 --> 00:29:38.880
I'm tired, I'm tired, let's sleep first.

00:29:39.519 --> 00:29:41.480
Sleep, sleep, sleep.

00:29:41.480 --> 00:29:42.880
Sleep, sleep.

00:29:42.880 --> 00:29:44.079
I'll make you sleep.

00:30:06.000 --> 00:30:06.759
Big Brother.

00:30:06.839 --> 00:30:08.039
You heard it the other day too, right?

00:30:08.039 --> 00:30:10.160
That guy from the next courtyard, three against one ganging up on Qiu,

00:30:11.039 --> 00:30:11.960
kicking Qiu

00:30:12.319 --> 00:30:15.240
out of our "Trident" group.

00:30:15.240 --> 00:30:16.319
He was kicked out long ago.

00:30:16.480 --> 00:30:17.400
Nice.

00:30:17.759 --> 00:30:18.759
A traitor

00:30:18.759 --> 00:30:20.319
never comes to a good end.

00:30:21.200 --> 00:30:22.359
You see, these rich people,

00:30:22.359 --> 00:30:24.160
how can they be so unscrupulous?

00:30:24.599 --> 00:30:25.720
That bastard Qiu,

00:30:25.720 --> 00:30:27.240
betrayed us for just one apartment.

00:30:27.559 --> 00:30:29.720
We can't let him knock us down with his money.

00:31:32.920 --> 00:31:33.759
What are you doing?

00:31:44.400 --> 00:31:46.559
I'm getting revenge on Ma Weiguo.

00:31:46.799 --> 00:31:48.400
What grudge do you have against him?

00:31:49.200 --> 00:31:50.440
It's because of him

00:31:50.440 --> 00:31:52.400
my dad went to prison back then.

00:31:52.400 --> 00:31:54.240
That's why his psychological trauma is so severe now,

00:31:54.240 --> 00:31:55.440
that's why he's become so twisted.

00:31:55.720 --> 00:31:56.960
So, tracing it back to the root,

00:31:56.960 --> 00:31:58.160
it's because of Ma Weiguo

00:31:58.160 --> 00:31:59.400
that my dad slapped me,

00:31:59.400 --> 00:32:00.279
that he hit me.

00:32:00.279 --> 00:32:02.440
You're digging way too deep for the root cause.

00:32:02.599 --> 00:32:04.160
So how do you plan to get revenge?

00:32:04.440 --> 00:32:05.720
I'm going to play a trick on him.

00:32:05.720 --> 00:32:07.079
There's a flue over there.

00:32:08.440 --> 00:32:10.759
I'm going to smash it open

00:32:10.759 --> 00:32:12.640
and then put the rats from our courtyard

00:32:13.440 --> 00:32:15.640
There are rats in the courtyard? Really?

00:32:15.640 --> 00:32:17.160
Of course there are rats in a single-story house.

00:32:17.279 --> 00:32:19.119
inside so they bite him at night.

00:32:19.200 --> 00:32:21.359
The rats, some are this small,

00:32:21.359 --> 00:32:22.680
and some are this big.

00:32:24.759 --> 00:32:25.400
What?

00:32:26.599 --> 00:32:28.720
Wang Chunsheng and his crew causing trouble wasn't enough,

00:32:29.279 --> 00:32:30.440
now it's your turn?

00:32:30.440 --> 00:32:31.680
Of course not me.

00:32:31.680 --> 00:32:32.920
I'm not involved at all.

00:32:35.519 --> 00:32:37.759
You think my dad and them are just making trouble for no reason?

00:32:38.039 --> 00:32:39.279
Then let me ask you,

00:32:39.559 --> 00:32:41.119
who in this alley actually welcomes you?

00:32:42.480 --> 00:32:43.319
Uncle Qiu's family?

00:32:43.440 --> 00:32:44.240
Our family?

00:32:44.880 --> 00:32:46.119
Ever since you came to this alley,

00:32:46.119 --> 00:32:47.680
there hasn't been a single peaceful day.

00:32:48.680 --> 00:32:50.039
As for your dad hitting you,

00:32:50.119 --> 00:32:51.400
that has absolutely nothing to do with me.

00:32:51.400 --> 00:32:52.519
How is it not related to you?

00:32:52.680 --> 00:32:53.440
If it weren't for you back then...

00:32:53.440 --> 00:32:55.039
You didn't even experience what happened back then.

00:32:55.200 --> 00:32:57.279
How do you know what your dad says is right?

00:32:58.039 --> 00:32:58.920
That's ridiculous.

00:32:58.920 --> 00:32:59.960
Do you think I should believe you,

00:32:59.960 --> 00:33:01.000
or believe my dad?

00:33:01.279 --> 00:33:02.240
Honestly.

00:33:03.039 --> 00:33:03.799
Hey, kid.

00:33:04.160 --> 00:33:04.839
What?

00:33:05.599 --> 00:33:06.519
Let's have a chat.

00:33:14.599 --> 00:33:15.200
Go on.

00:33:16.039 --> 00:33:17.240
The matters of the older generation...

00:33:17.240 --> 00:33:18.400
you shouldn't get involved.

00:33:18.920 --> 00:33:19.880
First of all,

00:33:20.319 --> 00:33:23.200
you need to decide what you want for your own future.

00:33:23.880 --> 00:33:24.519
Obviously.

00:33:24.640 --> 00:33:26.079
If I could decide for myself,

00:33:26.400 --> 00:33:28.000
would I be fighting with my dad?

00:33:29.079 --> 00:33:30.400
You don't want to go to college

00:33:30.400 --> 00:33:31.839
because whether you go or not,

00:33:31.839 --> 00:33:33.039
the future you see

00:33:33.039 --> 00:33:34.240
makes no difference.

00:33:34.480 --> 00:33:35.480
And your dad,

00:33:35.480 --> 00:33:36.559
keeps pushing you to go to college

00:33:36.559 --> 00:33:38.319
because he never went himself.

00:33:38.319 --> 00:33:39.599
So it's his obsession.

00:33:40.079 --> 00:33:42.279
Both of you are stuck in your own obsessions.

00:33:42.279 --> 00:33:44.160
That's why you can't communicate.

00:33:48.640 --> 00:33:49.799
That makes sense.

00:33:50.400 --> 00:33:51.519
Let's make a deal.

00:33:54.200 --> 00:33:55.359
An equal deal.

00:33:55.559 --> 00:33:56.680
Fair and square.

00:33:56.880 --> 00:33:57.799
She can be our witness.

00:33:58.720 --> 00:34:00.680
You? On what grounds?

00:34:00.799 --> 00:34:02.519
Even though I dislike my dad,

00:34:02.519 --> 00:34:04.519
I wouldn't go so far as to betray him.

00:34:20.880 --> 00:34:22.239
Why are you with him?

00:34:22.679 --> 00:34:24.280
Come over here. Sit down.

00:34:29.960 --> 00:34:31.760
Now I've thrown down the gauntlet.

00:34:31.760 --> 00:34:34.039
Next, I have to challenge you.

00:34:36.480 --> 00:34:38.239
I can solve Wang Fei's problem for you.

00:34:38.639 --> 00:34:40.239
He doesn't want to go to college, right?

00:34:40.320 --> 00:34:42.320
And he feels nothing is worth doing.

00:34:42.400 --> 00:34:43.519
I can help him.

00:34:44.840 --> 00:34:46.239
Are you out of your mind?

00:34:46.320 --> 00:34:47.559
He's my son.

00:34:47.880 --> 00:34:49.000
What do I need you for?

00:34:49.000 --> 00:34:49.599
Let me tell you something.

00:34:49.599 --> 00:34:50.679
Stay away from my son.

00:34:50.920 --> 00:34:51.840
No, Dad.

00:34:53.719 --> 00:34:55.199
I really want to give it a try with Third Uncle.

00:34:55.400 --> 00:34:56.280
Feifei.

00:34:57.360 --> 00:34:58.159
No, Second Uncle.

00:34:58.159 --> 00:34:59.159
That's not what I meant.

00:34:59.159 --> 00:35:00.320
I just want to see

00:35:00.320 --> 00:35:01.280
what he can possibly do to me.

00:35:01.280 --> 00:35:02.000
What? What did you say?

00:35:02.000 --> 00:35:03.480
You really want to try this with him?

00:35:03.639 --> 00:35:06.639
Yeah, let's give it a shot.

00:35:10.719 --> 00:35:13.039
How do you think you can help him?

00:35:13.039 --> 00:35:13.760
Big Brother.

00:35:13.760 --> 00:35:15.280
No, no, don't get upset yet.

00:35:15.960 --> 00:35:17.280
I'll do my best.

00:35:17.760 --> 00:35:19.119
If I help him,

00:35:19.280 --> 00:35:20.639
you agree to one condition of mine.

00:35:20.880 --> 00:35:23.039
First, let me hear what this condition is.

00:35:23.039 --> 00:35:24.679
If I succeed in helping Wang Fei,

00:35:24.840 --> 00:35:27.039
I want one of the shadow walls on the roof of Penglexuan.

00:35:27.039 --> 00:35:28.400
It will belong to me from then on.

00:35:29.519 --> 00:35:30.440
See?

00:35:30.960 --> 00:35:32.719
The conspiracy is coming to light right away.

00:35:33.119 --> 00:35:36.119
Trying to dismantle Penglexuan? No way.

00:35:36.119 --> 00:35:37.159
I only want the shadow wall.

00:35:37.320 --> 00:35:38.760
I don't want anything else.

00:35:38.760 --> 00:35:40.360
Not a single brick or tile of Penglexuan

00:35:40.360 --> 00:35:41.599
will be given to you.

00:35:42.800 --> 00:35:43.679
Alright then.

00:35:44.320 --> 00:35:45.679
Think it over carefully.

00:35:45.960 --> 00:35:48.840
Which is more important, a few bricks or your son?

00:35:49.119 --> 00:35:50.400
You figure it out for yourself.

00:35:52.519 --> 00:35:55.639
Are you insane?

00:35:55.639 --> 00:35:57.519
Big Brother, you see it now, right?

00:35:58.079 --> 00:35:59.760
His goal is still Penglexuan.

00:36:00.280 --> 00:36:02.440
No, you really want to try this with him?

00:36:02.440 --> 00:36:03.559
Why?

00:36:04.320 --> 00:36:05.119
Dad, I...

00:36:05.800 --> 00:36:07.199
I don't know why either.

00:36:07.639 --> 00:36:09.039
But didn't you say the other day,

00:36:09.440 --> 00:36:10.360
as long as I'm interested,

00:36:10.360 --> 00:36:11.559
you would support me?

00:36:12.239 --> 00:36:13.440
Well, right now, I just...

00:36:13.440 --> 00:36:14.599
I want to try it with him.

00:36:14.599 --> 00:36:16.320
I want to see what method he has.

00:36:17.239 --> 00:36:17.880
Second Uncle.

00:36:18.440 --> 00:36:20.599
I think Third Uncle is actually a good person.

00:36:20.679 --> 00:36:21.239
Really.

00:36:22.000 --> 00:36:23.400
Dad, I really want to try.

00:36:43.280 --> 00:36:44.119
Morning, Uncle.

00:36:46.079 --> 00:36:47.599
So where are we going today?

00:36:47.599 --> 00:36:48.719
You'll know in a bit.

00:36:49.960 --> 00:36:50.800
In a bit?

00:36:51.800 --> 00:36:53.440
You're being quite mysterious.

00:37:00.559 --> 00:37:02.519
What, are we walking there?

00:37:02.719 --> 00:37:03.960
Why so many questions?

00:37:04.760 --> 00:37:05.880
What are we going to do?

00:37:06.199 --> 00:37:07.360
Just follow me.

00:37:07.880 --> 00:37:08.920
So many questions.

00:37:15.320 --> 00:37:18.119
Third Uncle, you even rented a car?

00:37:18.320 --> 00:37:19.480
With a driver too?

00:37:19.599 --> 00:37:21.239
What, don't you like it?

00:37:22.079 --> 00:37:22.639
I like it.

00:37:22.880 --> 00:37:23.440
Get in.

00:37:26.119 --> 00:37:27.000
Driver, close the door.

00:37:58.800 --> 00:38:00.280
Now this is living.

00:38:00.280 --> 00:38:01.719
Don't get sentimental yet.

00:38:01.920 --> 00:38:03.199
The best part is still to come.

00:38:05.199 --> 00:38:07.199
So how exactly are you planning to help me?

00:38:07.719 --> 00:38:10.199
Your dad wants you to endure hardship, right?

00:38:10.440 --> 00:38:11.639
We'll do the opposite.

00:38:11.800 --> 00:38:13.000
I'll take you to enjoy life.

00:38:14.920 --> 00:38:17.559
Uncle, why didn't you come back sooner?

00:38:18.400 --> 00:38:19.280
This is great.

00:38:19.920 --> 00:38:20.920
Can I eat all of this?

00:38:20.920 --> 00:38:21.440
Eat.

00:38:24.760 --> 00:38:26.159
Off to enjoy life!

00:38:35.079 --> 00:38:36.239
Take this card.

00:38:36.559 --> 00:38:37.360
Use it freely.

00:38:38.159 --> 00:38:39.639
Anything money can solve

00:38:39.800 --> 00:38:40.840
is not a problem.

00:38:51.519 --> 00:38:52.440
Mr. Wang.

00:38:52.440 --> 00:38:54.320
You have successfully topped up fifty thousand yuan.

00:38:54.480 --> 00:38:55.679
Here is your bill.

00:38:55.679 --> 00:38:57.119
Enjoy your meal.

00:39:06.440 --> 00:39:07.320
Brother Fei, Brother Fei.

00:39:07.320 --> 00:39:09.119
Can I borrow your account to play next time?

00:39:09.119 --> 00:39:10.079
Godfather.

00:39:13.119 --> 00:39:13.800
Sure, Brother Fei.

00:39:13.800 --> 00:39:14.519
This piece is our

00:39:14.519 --> 00:39:16.599
autumn new arrival, the star player signature edition.

00:39:16.599 --> 00:39:19.159
We can see the signature embroidered in gold thread on the collar

00:39:19.159 --> 00:39:20.960
and the exclusive numbered nameplate.

00:39:20.960 --> 00:39:23.599
It's a global limited release of eight thousand pieces.

00:39:25.320 --> 00:39:26.400
Breakfast is served on the thirty-second floor

00:39:26.400 --> 00:39:27.920
at the Executive Lounge.

00:39:28.079 --> 00:39:28.880
Mr. Wang.

00:39:29.000 --> 00:39:31.280
Marriott International wishes you a pleasant stay.

00:39:51.079 --> 00:39:51.800
Take a look

00:39:53.199 --> 00:39:54.199
Come and get it

00:39:54.920 --> 00:39:55.880
These headphones

00:39:55.880 --> 00:39:58.039
not only have a great look and fit,

00:39:58.039 --> 00:39:58.440
but also

00:39:58.440 --> 00:39:59.800
This essence water I'm holding

00:39:59.800 --> 00:40:00.920
can provide the skin with

00:40:00.920 --> 00:40:02.519
ample nutrition and moisture.

00:40:02.519 --> 00:40:03.239
It hydrates effectively.

00:40:03.239 --> 00:40:04.480
What tier is Konglongniao in outdoor apparel?

00:40:04.480 --> 00:40:05.480
I don't need to say more.

00:40:05.480 --> 00:40:07.400
No need to worry about fakes, folks.

00:40:17.239 --> 00:40:18.159
Let me clarify.

00:40:18.639 --> 00:40:19.880
There won't be any

00:40:19.880 --> 00:40:21.599
ridiculous event like gold falling from the sky.

00:40:21.840 --> 00:40:22.960
So don't count on it.

00:40:23.519 --> 00:40:25.679
And if you see it, don't you dare copy it.

00:40:25.760 --> 00:40:27.119
As for the reason,

00:40:27.440 --> 00:40:28.679
it's not some grand philosophy.

00:40:29.320 --> 00:40:30.159
Just think about it.

00:40:30.559 --> 00:40:31.559
You're burning money,

00:40:31.800 --> 00:40:33.400
with a crowd cheering you on.

00:40:33.840 --> 00:40:35.519
Doesn't that look like watching a monkey show?

00:40:35.920 --> 00:40:37.360
Would anyone envy the monkey?

00:40:40.800 --> 00:40:41.440
Old Yang

00:40:41.559 --> 00:40:42.239
Coming.

00:40:42.480 --> 00:40:43.440
Get me ten tickets.

00:40:43.599 --> 00:40:44.880
Ten quick-pick tickets, right?

00:40:45.559 --> 00:40:48.320
Alright, ten quick-picks.

00:40:48.880 --> 00:40:50.639
I see your Feifei

00:40:50.639 --> 00:40:53.039
hanging out with Weiguo every single day.

00:40:53.039 --> 00:40:53.800
What's the deal?

00:40:53.800 --> 00:40:55.599
Did you give your son away to him?

00:40:55.599 --> 00:40:57.400
Cut the darn nonsense, will you?

00:40:57.400 --> 00:40:58.760
I sent you the money.

00:40:58.760 --> 00:40:59.360
Okay.

00:41:01.559 --> 00:41:02.679
Wait, tell me.

00:41:03.280 --> 00:41:05.400
Me handing my kid over to Weiguo,

00:41:06.559 --> 00:41:07.760
is that a reliable plan?

00:41:07.760 --> 00:41:09.199
It's fine, right?

00:41:10.119 --> 00:41:11.679
It's a huge problem!

00:41:11.679 --> 00:41:13.280
Bro, I was just looking for you.

00:41:13.599 --> 00:41:16.679
What? What's the problem?

00:41:16.880 --> 00:41:18.159
You've seen it yourself.

00:41:18.360 --> 00:41:19.920
Ma Weiguo's sugar-coated bullets

00:41:19.920 --> 00:41:21.079
are a fierce offensive.

00:41:21.280 --> 00:41:22.559
Feifei's just a kid.

00:41:22.559 --> 00:41:23.880
How can he resist that?

00:41:25.039 --> 00:41:26.280
I'm guessing

00:41:26.800 --> 00:41:28.280
your standing in Feifei's heart

00:41:28.280 --> 00:41:29.440
is lower than Ma Weiguo's now.

00:41:29.679 --> 00:41:32.440
I think Weiguo means no harm.

00:41:32.440 --> 00:41:34.440
He's spending real money.

00:41:35.079 --> 00:41:36.119
I just regret

00:41:36.119 --> 00:41:38.079
why I don't have a son, you know?

00:41:38.079 --> 00:41:39.519
Come on, have you ever seen a decent person

00:41:39.519 --> 00:41:40.840
educate a child like this?

00:41:40.840 --> 00:41:41.880
The thing is, I've never seen

00:41:41.880 --> 00:41:43.280
such a decently rich person either.

00:41:43.280 --> 00:41:44.199
Playing around like this every day,

00:41:44.199 --> 00:41:45.320
how can he focus on studying?

00:41:45.760 --> 00:41:46.360
Right.

00:41:47.719 --> 00:41:48.639
Bro.

00:41:48.639 --> 00:41:50.000
About this studying abroad thing,

00:41:50.000 --> 00:41:51.360
I've already made all the arrangements.

00:41:51.559 --> 00:41:52.440
If you don't need it,

00:41:52.440 --> 00:41:53.199
I'll just cancel it with them.

00:41:53.199 --> 00:41:54.400
No, no, no.

00:41:55.280 --> 00:41:56.880
I think the person you found

00:41:56.880 --> 00:41:58.119
is actually quite reliable.

00:41:58.239 --> 00:41:59.599
Of course he is.

00:41:59.599 --> 00:42:01.199
Feifei's education is a big deal.

00:42:02.360 --> 00:42:03.079
Yes.

00:42:08.840 --> 00:42:12.440
Wow, a Mercedes. A Maybach even, look.

00:42:15.719 --> 00:42:16.719
Wang Fei.